categories: Category:Imperial Army officers of the Galactic Empire

nodes.text: An officer served a commander in the Imperial Army as of 9 ABY. He served under General Freja Covell, who himself served Grand Admiral Thrawn's empire. The officer was deployed to Myrkr with a force of three All Terrain Armored Transports, one of which he commanded, the Number Four. His walker scanned Talon Karrde's Myrkr Base to give a report to the general.
